              <p class="text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed"><span class="text-[#9b7ab8] font-mono">switch(option)</span> — Routes the user to the appropriate action based on their menu selection. Each case handles its own validation before modifying the balance or transaction count.</p>
              <p class="text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed"><span class="text-[#9b7ab8] font-mono">Spend validation chain (case 3)</span> — The conditions are ordered intentionally: first check if the amount is zero or negative, then if it exceeds the P1000 limit, then if the balance is sufficient. Checking in this order ensures the most specific errors are caught before the general ones.</p>
